PARENT = TOPMOST CONTENT;
PARENTPADDY = IMMEDIATE TOP CONTENT

IF AN OBJECT HAS PARENT PADDY AND PARENT, IT IS A COMMENT.
IF PARENT PADDY IS EQUAL TO PARENT, IT IS A COMMENT

If an object has parentpaddy and parent .. it is a comment
if parentpaddy is equal to parent .. it is comment and the parent is a post, question or resource.. then get the parent
if parentpaddy is not equal to parent.. it is a reply to a comment .. get the parentpaddy